        <updateDate>2019-11-04T15:32:09Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Expanding Access to Apprenticeships Act</b></p> <p>This bill allows tax-free distributions from qualified tuition programs (known as 529 plans) to be used for certain expenses associated with registered apprenticeship programs.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
